&lt;li&gt;Oversee installation and operation of various mechanical systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead role in defining and developing the training, materials, and tools needed to support our chiller/HVAC maintenance business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be available to work some nights or weekends, on a rotating basis, to service emergency needs of our customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain good working order of company vehicle including refueling as necessary, reporting any mechanical issues. Vehicles should be washed on a regular basis. Proper stock, parts, tools, and safety equipment shall always be maintained in the vehicle.&lt;/li&gt;
