&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;With the Project Manager, understands the plans and specifications for assigned projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Alerts Project Manager of potential RFI (Request for Information) based on drawing and specification review and site conditions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinates the required resources to ensure tasks are done accurately, on time, and within the scope of the contract.
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicates the Project Manager for any issues, barriers, or concerns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluates the contractual scope of work.
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actively communicated opportunities for additional work to the Project Manager.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicates both technical and business-related issues with the customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review labor, material cost plans and specifications for work performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reviews equipment selections and submittals to be ordered, ensuring all meet contract requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinates equipment/material deliveries, responsible for equipment inspections upon delivery. Report any damage immediately.&lt;/li&gt;
